    "# Skill Gap Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "## Objective\n",
    "\n",
    "This section compares the skills possessed by our team members \n",
    "against the skills demanded by IT and data science job postings. \n",
    "By identifying gaps, we can develop targeted learning strategies.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Part 1: Team Skill Assessment\n",
    "\n",
    "### Current Skills of Team Members\n",
    "\n",
    "Our team conducted a self-assessment of technical skills relevant \n",
    "to data science and IT careers. We rated each skill on a scale of \n",
    "1-5, where:\n",
    "\n",
    "- **1 = Beginner:** No experience\n",
    "- **2 = Basic Knowledge:** Some exposure, limited application\n",
    "- **3 = Intermediate:** Can apply independently with occasional guidance\n",
    "- **4 = Advanced:** Proficient and comfortable teaching others\n",
    "- **5 = Expert:** Mastery level, could lead projects\n",
    "\n",
    "### Creating Our Skill DataFrame"
